#Counts are from all branches not just the HEAD

Number of files: git ls-files | wc -l
Total number of lines: git ls-files | xaras wc -l
List of branches: git branch (local), git branch -r (remote), git branch -a (all)
List of tags: git tag
List of committers: git log --format='%aN' | sort -u
Commits per author: git shortlog -sn --all
Commits per day: 
Number of commits: git shortlog --all | grep -E '^[ ]+\w+' | wc -l
Number of commits per branch: git rev-list --count <branch_name>

